Question: On which side of the image is the ball, the right or the left?

Reference Answer: right

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n574498.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=GET(image=IMAGE)
IMAGE0=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='ball')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'left' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'right'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
